# Cursor Runtime Core

- Treat `AGENTS.md` and `.agents/` as the source of truth.
- Read `.agents/README.md`, `.agents/RUNTIMES.md`, and `.agents/GUARDRAILS.md` before acting.
- Do not redefine workflow, profiles, quality gates, or routing in Cursor-specific files.
- If there is any conflict between `.cursor/rules` and `.agents/`, follow `.agents/`.
- Every multi-agent style task must preserve these artifacts:
  - `plan`
  - `patch_summary`
  - `verification_report`
